Title: Highland Grazing
Description: Wooly Cows are a special breed, enjoying colder temperatures and plenty of clean, fresh mountain air.

DescriptionTranslations.en-GB: Wooly Cows are a special breed, enjoying colder temperatures and plenty of clean, fresh mountain air.
